               <p>
                  <rs id="t17860719-59-punish285" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860719-59-punish285" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860719-59-defend634 t17860719-59-punish285"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
